Sheila Kennelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sheila_Kennelly 0 Sheila Kennelly (born 28 December 1927 in Marine Square, Brighton, Sussex, South East England), also credited as Sheila Kenneally, is a retired English Australian character actress of theatre, television and film, with a career spanning over 50 years in the industry. She is best known for her roles in TV soap operas and serials.
